<h2>Who needs residential Amazon Leo Internet in Kenya?</h2>

<p>Residential Amazon Leo Internet is most useful for homes where standard internet options are limited or frustrating. This includes rural homes without fibre, farms that need a fixed connection, peri-urban estates waiting for fibre expansion, holiday homes, remote worker homes, and houses where mobile data is expensive or inconsistent. It can also help families that need stable online learning, video calls, streaming, security cameras, and smart devices.</p>

