<p>Location affects cost. A simple Nairobi home with easy roof access is different from a rural property that needs travel, a pole mount, longer cable, and power backup. A maisonette may need mesh Wi-Fi. A farm residence may need an outdoor access point. A rented apartment may need a non-invasive mounting solution approved by the landlord or building manager.</p>

