<p>Residential customers should confirm the monthly payment process before installation. Know the billing cycle, account name, payment reference, support contact, and what happens if payment is late. If local M-Pesa payment is supported by your provider, verify the official details from the invoice or provider communication, not from forwarded screenshots.</p>

